latestIgtvVideos.title: Papa ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In the loving Memory of 🙏
𝐌𝐫. 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐨𝐣 𝐊𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐫 𝐒𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐡
 
A man who led his life without any fear and devoted his everything to friends & family , lived in a city but never got detached from his villagehood, whoever met or knew him had to say only one thing “ Yaar Manoj ji / Thakur sahab insaan ho toh tumhare jaisa ek dum madmast”.

You used to ask me every time whom do i love the most - It’s you Papa , It has always been you and it’ll always be you!

Your sacrifices, your teachings , Your guidance everything is imprinted in your children. 
We can never and we will never forget what all you did to keep your family happy & protected all the time.

We miss you  We all miss you !😔

- Juhi , Ranu & Nikku 
(Apke teen anmol Ratan)

Audio - @_musafir31

latestPosts.caption:
Wrapping up this trip to Rudraprayag with a full heart and a mind buzzing with stories, feelings, and moments I’ll hold onto for a long time. This place felt like something out of a forgotten chapter, quietly powerful and deeply grounding.

There’s a reason Uttarakhand is called Devbhoomi. Every step here feels like you’re walking through centuries of faith, history, and nature working in sync. I came back with more than just photos.I came back with questions, answers, peace, and a kind of wonder I didn’t know I needed.

Huge thank you to @uttarakhand_tourismofficial for making this experience possible — for opening doors to places and stories that don’t just stay with you, they change you.

If you ever feel the need to disconnect to reconnect,come here. Let the mountains do their thing.
